OL,3,CBits of tar sticking to tyres and
OL,4,Cshoes as road melts in heatwave
OL,6,FA road is melting in the heatwave,
OL,7,Fwith bits of tar sticking to tyres and
OL,8,Feven to flip flops, residents have
OL,9,Fcomplained.
OL,11,FResidents in Cannock town in
OL,12,FStaffordshire, said it is a safety
OL,13,Frisk, and it is causing expensive
OL,14,Fdamage to their tyres and driveways in
OL,15,FGorsemoor Road.
OL,17,FThe highways authority said it is
OL,18,Fseeing whether it needs to temporarily
OL,19,Fclose the road, and has been out on
OL,20,FFriday and Saturday to treat it.
