OL,3,CBits of tar sticking to tyres and
OL,4,Cshoes as road melts in heatwave
OL,6,F"You're ripping up great big chunks
OL,7,Fout of the road and when you put the
OL,8,Fcar onto the drive, it's literally
OL,9,Fbringing all the tar onto the drives
OL,10,Fand it's just spreading all over
OL,11,Fthem," said Marc Edwards.
OL,13,FHe and his family have been watching
OL,14,Fas drivers fall foul to the sticky
OL,15,Fsurface.
OL,17,FHe continued: "It's wrecking loads of
OL,18,Fpeople's drives all up and down the
OL,19,Fstreet, and and obviously with the
OL,20,Ftyre issues as well, it's condensing
OL,21,Fon tyres overnight."
