OL,6,FOne resident has been quoted #300 to
OL,7,Frepair her tyres, which are covered in
OL,8,Ftarmac and stones from the road.
OL,10,F"A lady was crossing the street and
OL,11,Fher flipflop got stuck in the tarmac
OL,12,Fand it almost came off," Josh Newbury,
OL,13,FMP for Cannock Chase said.
OL,15,F"It caused her to trip. A car had to
OL,16,Fdo an emergency stop to not hit her.
OL,17,FIt just shows it's not just motorists
OL,18,Fat risk, it's also pedestrians."
