OL,6,FResident Shaun Dennis said he has only
OL,7,Fbeen using his car early in the
OL,8,Fmorning or late at night since the
OL,9,Froad started melting.
OL,11,FHe said: "It's quite shocking after
OL,12,Fbeing recently renewed. Motorways
OL,13,Fdon't melt, roads in Spain don't melt,
OL,14,Fcertain roads that you drive on in
OL,15,Fthis temperature aren't melting.
OL,17,F"So there's obviously something
OL,18,Ffundamental about the work that's been
OL,19,Fdone here."
