OL,6,FPeter Mason, Staffordshire County
OL,7,FCouncil's Cabinet Member for Strategic
OL,8,FHighways, said: "We are aware of the
OL,9,Fcurrent condition of Gorsemoor Road in
OL,10,FCannock and have been working closely
OL,11,Fwith our contractors to address the
OL,12,Fissue as a priority.
