OL,6,F"As you'll be aware, an amber heat
OL,7,Fhealth alert is currently in place. A
OL,8,Fsunny day in the 20Cs can be enough to
OL,9,Fgenerate 50C on the dark asphalt road
OL,10,Fsurfaces. Over the weekend,
OL,11,Ftemperatures in Staffordshire are
OL,12,Freaching over 30C, significantly
OL,13,Fincreasing the risk of surface melting
OL,14,Fon newly laid roads.
