OL,6,F"Yesterday, we deployed a gritter to
OL,7,Ftreat the road with granite dust. This
OL,8,Fhelps absorb the softened bitumen and
OL,9,Fimproves grip for vehicles using the
OL,10,Froad. This afternoon, a second
OL,11,Fapplication of granite dust has been
OL,12,Fcarried out, and an inspector is also
OL,13,Fvisiting site today to assess whether
OL,14,Fa temporary road closure is needed to
OL,15,Fensure safety for all road users.
OL,17,F"We'd like to thank residents and
OL,18,Fdrivers for their patience while we
OL,19,Fwork to manage the impact of these
OL,20,Fhigh temperatures on the road network."
